album.title: Who Want Smoke?? (feat. G Herbo, Lil Durk & 21 Savage) - Single

wiki.summary: For the remix of his breakout single, Nardo Wick enlists the help of recording artists Lil Durk, 21 Savage and G Herbo, and Cole Benett for the song’s visuals. With a Chicago drill cadence, Lil Durk takes the opportunity to respond to those telling him to “Slide for Von” online whilst discussing the levels of violence and potential criminality involved in his lifestyle, alongside everyone else featured. wiki.content: For the remix of his breakout single, Nardo Wick enlists the help of recording artists Lil Durk, 21 Savage and G Herbo, and Cole Benett for the song’s visuals. With a Chicago drill cadence, Lil Durk takes the opportunity to respond to those telling him to “Slide for Von” online whilst discussing the levels of violence and potential criminality involved in his lifestyle, alongside everyone else featured. The conclusion of 21 Savage’s verse garnered viral acclaim through TikTok and other socials – accumulating 139,200 videos as of November 2021. Read more on Last.fm.
